            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="content">
            <p class="bodytext">A more effective UI design that allows for UX students in the program to showcase their work, while also granting more info for perspective students.</p>
            <a href="#" class="subheadpink">#userinterfacedesign</a> <a href="#" class="subheadpink">#userexperience</a>
